The paper deals with security and privacy issues in mobile authentication systems, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques for sensor fusion, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the feasibility of manipulating sensor readings, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and system and control theory (cs.SD).
